    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，不管是YES还是NO都先经过C Crowd。这个设计是为了让人工复核自动分类的结果，避免漏判。C Crowd审核之后，再决定是更新分类器模型，还是把事件写回Crossref。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER",
        "C_CROWD",
        "CLASSIFIER_TRAINER",
        "ADD_EVENT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把C Crowd画成菱形判断节点，然后分出两条分支：一条指向Classifier Trainer用于模型更新，另一条指向Add event to Crossref。两条分支都是YES条件触发吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C_CROWD",
        "CLASSIFIER_TRAINER",
        "ADD_EVENT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，C Crowd审核通过的样本，一部分用来训练更新自动分类器，另一部分确认是有效事件的就直接添加到Crossref。另外，Classifier Trainer更新完模型后，要把更新反馈回Auto Classifier，形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C_CROWD",
        "CLASSIFIER_TRAINER",
        "ADD_EVENT",
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。我检查一下：Samples from Crossref进入Auto Classifier，分出YES/NO都到C Crowd；C Crowd再分两路，一路Update回到Auto Classifier，一路Add event to Crossref。闭环结构应该完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SAMPLES_FROM_CROSSREF",
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER",
        "C_CROWD",
        "CLASSIFIER_TRAINER",
        "ADD_EVENT"
